<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/283373-i-m-big-into-stephen-king-favorites-pet">I&#39;m big into Stephen King. Favorites: Pet Sematary, IT, and Thinner (yeah I know, weird third choice. Just something Inexplicable about Thinner that I love.) I also love Four Past Midnight and The Shining. 

Do you think I will enjoy Straub? This novel in particular?</a>
</div>
