        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2602053609" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer14071457833632120468">This is one of the scariest books I’ve ever come across. The atmosphere is often creepy and foreboding, and some of the occurrences are downright disturbing. If you like horror this is probably right up your alley. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


